      "writtenOn": "2018-11-08T01:03:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Tangentially, would you accept a CL to combine SkRawAdapterCodec and SkWebpAdapterCodec into a single SkAndroidCodecAdapter class? There doesn\u0027t seem much RAW- or WebP-specific to those two separate implementations, and if there was a common one, I wouldn\u0027t have to write a separate SkWuffsAdapterCodec.",
